# sphinx-disqus

Embed [Disqus](https://disqus.com) comments in Sphinx documents/pages.

* Python 3.9 through 3.12 supported on Linux, macOS, and Windows.

ðŸ“– Full documentation: https://sphinx-disqus.readthedocs.io

